name: The Classic
description:
Fully refined. 

Dark tan leather straps, base and trim. Grey waterproof canvas outer and cream canvas inner. 

The HA interpretation of the traditional Alpine backpack. 

Built for durability, weather in the urban environment or on the mountainside. HA has selected the best materials from around the world and married them with the hardest construction. 

For more on the story of this product please visit:

www.hawebsite.com and click on PROJECT 2// HA accessories Range


Size: 450mm by 380mm by 110mm
